title: Game won't finish.
body:
after a game I couldn't see the result page. I relogged, and it says I am still in a game. 
Can't even reconnect to the finished game(of course it is finished).
It has been like this for like 10 minutes.
What's going on Riot.

replies.body: 30 minute now ,same here , cant play another game {{champion:157}}
